"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/419228","Cabinet Office","false","2015-09-25","<p>The information requested falls within the responsibility of the UK Statistics Authority. I have asked the Authority to reply.</p>",,"Lord Bridges of Headley","HL2302","2015-09-25T12:22:56.53Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/419228/answer","Biography information for Lord Bridges of Headley","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/419228/answer","HL2301 & HL2302 Lord Roberts UKSA Reply.pdf","HL2301 & HL2302 Lord Roberts UKSA Reply.pdf","UK Statistics Reply ","UK Statistics Reply ","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/419228/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2015-09-16","Vacancies","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government what is their estimate of the number of current job vacancies in each region in England.","false","Biography information for Lord Roberts of Llandudno",,"Lord Roberts of Llandudno","HL2301"
